{"tid":205392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為食女立志做醫生","createTime":"2017-04-17T17:56:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T20:26:14.000Z","uid":5195,"like":260,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"aa5d58e8226ca1b0c3448919325c2ce4f44cb5a2","tid":205392,"uid":5195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T17:56:33.000Z","msg":"為食女立志做醫生<br />\n【本報訊】協恩中學的女狀元陳詠妍除了7科考獲5**級外，在數學科的延伸部分亦考獲5**級，成為超級女狀元，對理科有濃厚興趣的她原來是「食得之人」，中五時已開始在社交網站Instagram寫食評，更有逾六百名追隨者，下至街邊數元小食、上至花費數千元的高級法國菜，詠妍也品嘗過，亦饒有心得，「最鍾意食分子料理，覺得好有創意！」冀將來考入醫科，「食好嘢要使錢，都要識搵錢至得。」<br />\n<img src=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20140715/photo/0715-00407-009b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20140715%2Fphoto%2F0715-00407-009b1.jpg&h=dd9d9b51&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2d5bc2c8dfb01c8e30939dbe32bc5eebea4fa1c","tid":205392,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T17:57:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n為 食女"},{"pid":"88c81b46be1706ae4e109e5dca11b057b3388d5a","tid":205392,"uid":3656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T17:58:23.000Z","msg":"我理解咗做，為&middot;食女，立志做醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e525a42db663c88bf8ced24940865a0926a122","tid":205392,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T17:58:24.000Z","msg":"為，食女，立志做醫生<br />\n為食，女，立志做醫生"},{"pid":"2df9189142dc6af9a4898e1074a6c97a36dcf2d2","tid":205392,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T17:59:30.000Z","msg":"...."},{"pid":"205ca1421b7d19e27c87ebd92a6d6e2ad8ef1f77","tid":205392,"uid":94835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T18:00:38.000Z","msg":"有冇人知佢做咗醫生咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55f369fd604013446