f72201e6550c35fbf4f1a01ce6cd531","tid":205392,"uid":35101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T06:59:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>求ig</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6ddb77bf73055052c846379fd4bc980ebcb1c8","tid":205392,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T14:29:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/18/143901_23f8ea1270631b1ed18543ce3aa0d641.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2F143901_23f8ea1270631b1ed18543ce3aa0d641.jpg&h=dd8fa75c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c5dbf809dfd08b0331b118d5e30f8498f7b7ef","tid":205392,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T14:53:31.000Z","msg":"其實第一個應該係果句乜乜 天下雨, 客人留不留<br />\n<br />\n有好多個意思"},{"pid":"dfac9338df1230fd4594cff26984d71df0c4a595","tid":205392,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T14:54:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實第一個應該係果句乜乜 天下雨, 客人留不留<br />\n<br />\n有好多個意思</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個<br />\n<br />\n下雨天留客天留我不留<br />\n<br />\n這句句子的基本拆解意思<br />\n下雨天留客，天留我不留<br />\n下雨天，留客天，留我不？留<br />\n兩句句子中的意思完全相反，在客人留給主人家的字條中被主人誤讀，於是主人送客，令客人無棲身之地。<br />\n<br />\n七種拆解方式，見於劉玉琛《標點符號用法》<br />\n下雨天留客，天留我不留。<br />\n下雨天留客，天留我？不留。<br />\n下雨天留客，天留我不？留。<br />\n下雨，天留客；天留我不留！<br />\n下雨天，留客天，留我？不留。<br />\n下雨天，留客天，留我不？留。<br />\n下雨天，留客天，留我不留？"},{"pid":"80450cb9d497d7b454f1c104e1e42852ed55e922","tid":205392,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T17:30:48.000Z","msg":"old news咁多人未睇過<br />\n連登好多細路仔🙄"},{"pid":"1bae933f23ee8762104b0d7ccdd8ce13abe5aa68","tid":205392,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T17:33:09.000Z","msg":"有志氣<br />\n<br />\n為左食女, 立志做醫生<br />\n做左醫生, 真係多到食唔晒啦"},{"pid":"04aff25c6ba55e3253b15c6f7f3a6cfe3e7d5e97","tid":205392,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T19:09:57.000Z","msg":"睇過曬但都仲係咁好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}